主要翻译
 
peasant n (poor farm person)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 农民 nóng mín TC Traditional Chinese 農民  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 农夫 nóng mín，nóng fū TC Traditional Chinese 農夫 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 村姑 nóng mín，cūn gū 
 -- There used to be many peasants in the English countryside.
 -- 英国乡村中从前有许多农民。

其他翻译
 
peasant n informal, pejorative (uncultured person)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 粗俗的人 cū sú de rén  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 粗鲁的人 cū sú de rén，cū lǔ de rén TC Traditional Chinese 粗魯的人 
 -- Gavin's manners are awful; he's such a peasant.

复合形式： 
 
peasant revolt, peasants' revolt n (uprising by poor workers)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 农民起义 nóng mín qǐ yì TC Traditional Chinese 農民起義  
 -- The French Revolution is a prime example of a peasant revolt.

